hopobject.body: We'd like to offer you the job doxycycline rite aid The Commons health select committee is going to review the operation of NHS 111. It must grasp the nettle and state plainly that applying the business approach to efficiency – substituting capital for labour, and substituting cheap labour for more expensive labour – can't be done safely in healthcare. But the provision of NHS 111 has been outsourced to a variety of providers with contracts that could be costly to terminate. Unless the public gets angry enough to force a rethink we had better hope that at least the computer stays risk-averse. Otherwise we must expect a growing number of "serious untoward incidents", in which some people will die.
